'''黄精明'''（英文: Jackson Ng），英国商业及诉讼事务律师，英国出庭[[大律师|大律师]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.legal500.com/firms/9442-chambers-of-lawrence-power/9442-london-england/lawyers/1120481-jackson-ng/|title=Jackson Ng > Chambers of Lawrence Power > London > England - Lawyer Profile|website=www.legal500.com}}</ref>，英国杰昂律师事务所合伙人<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.jacksonlyon.com/ourteamcn |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-11-17 |archive-date=2020-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026100818/https://www.jacksonlyon.com/ourteamcn |dead-url=no }}</ref>，英国政治人物。現為[[比肯斯菲尔德|比肯斯菲尔德]]镇议会议员<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.beaconsfieldconservatives.co.uk/people/jackson-ng|title=Jackson Ng|website=Beaconsfield}}</ref>， 以及当地小学校董<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.butlerscourt.bucks.sch.uk/our-governors/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-11-01 |archive-date=2020-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929001545/https://www.butlerscourt.bucks.sch.uk/our-governors/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。该镇是英国最富有的城镇之一<ref>{{cite web|url=//https://www.standard.co.uk/news/uk/england-most-expensive-cheapest-market-towns-home-buyers-b939909.html?amp|title=England’s most and least expensive market towns for home buyers revealed|date=2021-06-10}}</ref>。黄精明同时也是[[上议院|上议院]][[韦鸣恩勋爵|韦鸣恩勋爵]]的政治顾问<ref name="bbc.com">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/ukchina/simp/uk_life/2015/03/150330_election_chinese_candidates|title=英国大选：华裔议员候选人一览表|date=2015-03-30|website=BBC 英伦网}}</ref>和保守党华人之友组织（CFOC）总干事<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.neehao.co.uk/the-board-of-the-conservative-friends-of-the-chinese-cfoc-announce-two-new-co-directors/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-11-01 |archive-date=2020-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921025348/https://www.neehao.co.uk/the-board-of-the-conservative-friends-of-the-chinese-cfoc-announce-two-new-co-directors/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2015年，2017年以及2019年，黄精明三次代表保守党参与了英国大选。<ref name="bbc.com"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oushinet.com/wap/qj/qjnews/20170603/263942.html|title=7位华裔候选人“打”入英国大选_欧时WAP|website=www.oushinet.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2017-06-01/doc-ifyfuvpm6906332.shtml|title=逐梦的英国华裔议员候选人|first=|last=经济参考报|date=2017-06-01|website=finance.sina.com.cn}}</ref>

黄精明先后在英国[[伦敦大学|伦敦大学]]亚非学院<ref>{{cite web|url=https://study.soas.ac.uk/soas-grads-election/|title=Can you guess which single party four SOAS grads are representing in the election?|date=2017-05-19|publisher=}}</ref>与[[伦敦政治经济学院|伦敦政治经济学院]]攻读法律专业，曾担任伦敦政经学院的研究员<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ccpn-global.org/team-members-at-lse|title=Team members at LSE|website=www.ccpn-global.org}}</ref>，之后成为英国执业的事务律师，后成为英国出庭大律师。

黄精明曾代理“英国伯明翰警员“不小心驾驶”撞死中国留学生张某一案”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ihuawen.com/index.php?g=&m=article&a=index&id=40854&cid=45|title=伯明翰被撞留学生事件后续报道 张轩玮父母：儿子被撞飞26米 警车严重超速 今日华闻|website=www.ihuawen.com}}</ref>，以及“中国女乘客乘维珍航班受辱事件”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.afinance.cn/new/shxw/201603/1088154.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-11-17 |archive-date=2017-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170702040328/http://www.afinance.cn/new/shxw/201603/1088154.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

黄精明于2020年10月接受了凤凰网关于中英日后环保合作走向的采访<ref>{{cite web|url=https://v.ifeng.com/c/80JrczXdFND|title=英国政府计划疫后力推清洁能源|website=v.ifeng.com}}</ref>。

2021年5月8日，Jackson Ng（ 黄精明）再次代表比肯斯菲尔德地区受选为英国白金汉郡地方议会的议员<ref>{{cite news |author1=Shruti Sheth Trivedi |title=Possible contenders for Buckinghamshire Council leader |url=https://www.bucksfreepress.co.uk/news/19292754.possible-contenders-buckinghamshire-council-leader/ |work=Bucks Free Press}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=华人律师当选英国白金汉宫郡地方议会议员！ |url=https://www.ukjs.co.uk/post/%E5%8D%8E%E4%BA%BA%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%88%E5%BD%93%E9%80%89%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E7%99%BD%E9%87%91%E6%B1%89%E5%AE%AB%E9%83%A1%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E8%AE%AE%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%AE%E5%91%98%EF%BC%81 |work=英国侨报}}</ref>。

2021年5月11日，黄精明和其合伙人蔡汝安（Leon Chua）代理的波及百位中国投资人的“Maxwell中国投资人诉英国内政部”一案，于英国上诉法院宣告胜诉<ref>{{cite web |title=£100 million investment visa loan scheme ruled legal after all |url=https://www.freemovement.org.uk/100-million-investment-visa-loan-scheme-ruled-legal-after-all/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=THE QUEEN ON THE APPLICATION OF JIE WANG AND ANOTHER  - and –   SECRETARY OF STATE FOR THE HOME DEPARTMENT |url=https://www.bailii.org/cgi-bin/format.cgi?doc=/ew/cases/EWCA/Civ/2021/679.html&query=(THE)+AND+(QUEEN)+AND+(ON)+AND+(THE)+AND+(APPLICATION)+AND+(OF)+AND+(JIE)+AND+(WANG)+AND+(ANOTHER) |website=British and Irish Legal Information Institute}}</ref>。

